metadata.name: PUNISH #1
metadata.description: "PUNISH" is the first audio-visual artwork from the upcoming Pussy Riot project that introduces a super(s)hero character who owns magic superwoman-like qualities & uses these powers to fight sexism. She's a strong dominatrix figure and serves justice by punishing weinsteins of the world. PUNISH talks about the vengeful shero spreading, and now men are scared to misbehave, because they're well aware that the revenge is coming.
